  "title": "Cook/Chef de Partie (West Area)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Location: West Area, Singapore</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Working Hours: 5-day work week (Permanent Sunday Off)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Monthly Salary: Up to S$2.8K (Negotiable)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and cook dishes according to the restaurant’s standards and recipes.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that food preparation and presentation are consistent and of high quality.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene in the kitchen at all times.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven experience as a Cook or Chef de Partie in a professional kitchen (seafood or modern cuisine experience is a plus).</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of kitchen operations and food safety standards.</li>\n  <li>Team player with a good attitude and willingness to learn.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Nextbeat Singapore Pte. Ltd.</p>\n<p>EA License Number: 22C1267</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22107133</p>",
